text: Andrew Withers (born 5 February 1957) is an Australian rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. He also competed in 1979 World Rowing Championships in Bled. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
